data.description: *HUGE PRICE REDUCTION! We are pleased to offer this unique property in the heart of Brentwood providing you a rare opportunity to have plenty of land right at the border of the the nation’s Capital. This 1917 Sears and Roebuck kit home has 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms and all of the rooms are extraordinarily spacious. But without a doubt, the leading feature of this property is LAND! Offered at $599,000, you get the home on 0.23 acres and in ADDITION this home is being sold with an adjoining additional lot directly behind it allowing access to this property from both Upshur St. and Jackson Ave. (Adjoining lot, behind the house,  also conveys with sale) Perfect opportunity for a buyer with lots of yard space or a builder who wants to subdivide and build! House needs some updating and is an estate sale.
